{"type": "article", "id": 38119, "title": "这张游乐场门票真的是名片？｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-02-23T23:36:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 37967, "name": "Whipping Post"}, {"id": 37968, "name": "Y"}, {"id": 37969, "name": "Carosello Lab"}, {"id": 37970, "name": "Stefano Bolcato"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 274, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170223223043hI9zbFJ3wlmxBTXq.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Business card by Carosello Lab</h3><p>如果说光凭名片就能对一家创意公司的创造力做出大致的判断，意大利创意机构 <a href=\"http://www.carosellolab.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Carosello Lab</a> 所使用的这套<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/46626697/CaroselloLab-Business-cards\" rel=\"nofollow\">名片</a>称得上是赢在起跑线上的那一类。它的排版和样式都借鉴了复古的游乐园门票，长长的一串在分发时还需要额外的一扯，很难不吸引到客户的注意力。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170223223017ASHsNfwntaCObm01.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170223223017VFUgvqeoS6B47EwO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170223223017OA62p1UwdyitKcEh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.672500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170223223017cuqUBvsKrYnhjH4T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.728333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702232230168rLtCFYXTKn74Psp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.490000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Paper Water Bottle</h3><p>“所以你制造垃圾？”十年前，当美国的产品包装设计师 Jim Warner 指着街边废弃的塑料水瓶向儿子解释自己的工作时，儿子的这句回答让他意识到自己应该利用专业所长，让下一代生活的环境少一些污染。为此，他组建了设计团队，成功研发出一款可以分解的环保水瓶。Paper Water Bottle 的瓶身由有机材质和可再生纤维（竹子、蒲草和甘蔗）构成，可回收树脂制成的内壁则保证了它的密封性。首批环保水瓶的容量均为 500 毫升，将以装满水的状态运送。目前单组（12 个）的运送仅限美国境内，其他地区的用户只能参与为期半年的订购计划（每月寄送 6 组，共 432 个）。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/paperwaterbottle/paper-water-bottle-we-will-help-save-our-planet\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，价格为 250 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702232228000sBXp5ybaljg3zT8.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702232228007kQuv3eZHO5XjEhY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170223222800Xz2bO45xwnMQLdSW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Straight Pen by LAINOVA</h3><p>没有尺的情况下，你能仅靠一支笔就画出笔直的线条吗？由韩国设计团队 LAINOVA 带来的双头笔 Straight Pen 通过在笔尖两侧设置滚轮，造福了希望提高效率的“手残党”。它的一头是常规的 0.5 毫米笔尖，位于末端的笔尖则需要推动开关解锁后才会弹出，随后只要稍许施力让两边的轮子和笔尖同时接触纸面，就能画出完美的直线了。要画出流畅的曲线也很方便，只要调节两个轮子的受力即可。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/straight-pen-art-design#/\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，单价为 9 美元一组（三根）。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170223222817q2naHCTI0rutPLpf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.698387\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170223222818M6kQW17rUHOaBtT3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.814516\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170223222817K735ZT6rchEj8W9w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667742\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170223222817W3TEdphJ42nM69Oj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.479032\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170223222818T6B7yDKjEuZniq21.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.770968\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Passport Wallet by Whipping Post</h3><p><a href=\"https://whippingpost.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Whipping Post</a> 是一个来自美国亚特兰大的皮具品牌，创始人 Ryan Barr 在转行后以制作吉他背带起步，陆续把产品线扩大到了各式各样的包具。这款以植鞣革制成的护照夹是 Whipping Post 的最新产品，它的构造相当简洁，除了烫金字体外的装饰只有随时间增加而产生的痕迹，和护照一起见证了每一场远行。这是它的<a href=\"https://whippingpost.com/collections/wallets/products/the-passport-wallet\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 55 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170223222835X4WMSpuBQo06mGUb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.890971\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170223222835G4z68tuRy1mfgxsT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.890971\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170223222835Dw4KnamfkUXC86MP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.890971\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170223222836IJdCVivKG2XnBW9Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.680412\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170223222836idjZ5gz74FQb9yc3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.890971\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Y002 by Y</h3><p>如果你不得不带衣架出行，会发现尽管大部分衣架都很扁平，它们所占的面积对有限的打包空间来说还不够友好。为了让衣架的大小也能变得“收放自如”，日本设计品牌 Y 推出了由两个木制组件和一根皮革绳组成的 Y002 衣架，细细的一圈可以轻松地放进包中，使用时只要随手一拉就能展开。美中不足的是，如果用它在潮湿的环境中晾衣服的话，有可能会让衣服沾染上皮革的痕迹。这是它的<a href=\"https://monoco.jp/brand/y/52457?cat_id=9\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 3240 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702232228505eqjLzTOSGA6v27D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.684091\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170223222850R8U742D9mBlPvIQr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170223222850ukipfZIaq5cv6x7d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702232228506N47ab9WxzEkg0cB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170223222851IdRf3UlT7pB0V5O8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>LEGO Iconic Paintings by Stefano Bolcato</h3><p>来自意大利的 <a href=\"http://www.stefanobolcato.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Stefano Bolcato</a> 是一位热衷于以乐高玩具进行创作的艺术家，和其他常见的衍生作品不同的是，Bolcato 更喜欢用绘画而非拼搭的方式呈现出一种奇特的穿越感。最近他就将一批画中人替换成了乐高小人，其中包括弗里达的自画像以及安迪·沃霍尔那幅经典的玛丽莲梦露。为了让这些作品看起来更逼真，Bolcato 特意保持了油画的形式。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170223222909s10ouyOTwEcXKxq3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334444\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170223222909N1XvgaIlzD6ht5sp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.355556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170223222909ho6rGgYTSKy9jlQA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.998889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170223222908YheTHo3j2JiMZaQt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.350000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170223222909t0D1Ld3FfoCNzkZq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.356667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170223222909vZkOtARfV3cLYW60.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666993\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}